    "attributes": {
        "action": "Apply tobacco advertising restrictions to vaping products",
        "additional_details": "I was driving down the road today and I saw a huge billboard advertising a new Flavour of vape. It really rubbed me the wrong way because a drove past a secondary school just before then and the amount of vapes I saw I thought was was disgusting. \r\n \r\nI think that the advertisement could be one reason that they get \u201chooked\u201d.\r\nI believe it would make a difference if vapes were treated like cigarettes in terms of advertising regulations.",
        "background": "I would like the Government to ban advertising vapes to the public. I would like vapes to be treated the same as a cigarettes in terms of advertising.",
